body:
Masterlist

SMUT *

REQUESTED #

~~~

Harry Styles:

Drabbles:

#1. Harry takes care of his girlfriend when she is sick.

#2. Harry’s girlfriend takes care of him when he is sick.

#3. Meeting Harry in Starbucks.

Imagines:

#1. Harry helps you when you are having a hard time sleeping and begin to feel unwell.

#2. Harry forgets your birthday.

*#3. Harry pleasing himself leads to much more.

*#4. Breakfast and something extra

#5. Power outages and cuddles

One-shots:

*You Are Mine: What happens when Harry’s girlfriend just so happens to be Zayn’s ex and he finds out about the songs he has written for her?

10 Things I Hate Love About You: Y/N writes a list of reasons she loves Harry and he just so happens to discover it. (Idea credit to @harrysniallpolish )

*‘Songbird’: Harry and Y/N have feelings for one another that come to fruition one fateful night.

Chaptered:

Tell Me Come Morning: With alcohol fueling Harry forward things begin to get interesting when he meets a beautiful stranger in the bar. (Part 2)

Collaborations

Asks

***

  • Dance appreciation post

title: My brother came to visit
body:
My brother: What have you been doing recently? Studying?
Me: Listening to music, mainly. 
Bro: What music?
Me: Harry Styles. Don't make fun of me though.
Bro: This gay?
Me: What?
Bro: He's gay. So is Zayn.
